{"type": "article", "id": 19557, "title": "可活动靠背的座椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-23T07:37:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 88, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134735SAIkKT09up46Leqs.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这把椅子带有一个可活动的靠背。可以旋转到与地面平行的位置，成为一张小桌，很适合当电脑桌面。椅子下面只有 3 根腿，人也需要随着椅子而转动到后面使用。此外，靠背和座位都是梯形的，可以将两张椅子的桌面前后拼在一起，成为可以讨论的桌子。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150032IKdq5lFhRiWJAOVw.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"788\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150033GLZKJvDOdTxgejb4.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"788\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150034XNnyzgBxasjmPkqw.jpg\" width=\"470\" height=\"256\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.54468085\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150034Lait4VNYOuIQE1fc.jpg\" width=\"470\" height=\"256\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.54468085\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}